      <title>T-Mobile 斥资 24 亿美元收购美国蜂窝资产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-28/t-mobile-scoops-up-us-cellular-assets-for-2-4-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国第二大移动运营商 T-Mobile US Inc. 已同意以约 24 亿美元收购 US Cellular Corp. 的无线业务及其部分频谱资产。彭博社的 Lynn Doan 报道。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-28/t-mobile-scoops-up-us-cellular-assets-for-2-4-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 18:18:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
